        <title type="html"><![CDATA[并查集学习笔记]]></title>
        <id>https://Sept0913.github.io/post/union-checking-set/</id>
        <link href="https://Sept0913.github.io/post/union-checking-set/">
        </link>
        <updated>2020-03-24T13:35:28.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.10.1/dist/katex.min.css">
<script defer src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.10.1/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
<p>从 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mn mathvariant="monospace">2020.01.22</mn></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\tt 2020.01.22</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.61111em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathtt">2</span><span class="mord mathtt">0</span><span class="mord mathtt">2</span><span class="mord mathtt">0</span><span class="mord mathtt">.</span><span class="mord mathtt">0</span><span class="mord mathtt">1</span><span class="mord mathtt">.</span><span class="mord mathtt">2</span><span class="mord mathtt">2</span></span></span></span></span> 起开始攻并查集，正是靠并查集我才混到了人生第一道<span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mstyle mathcolor="Blue"><mi mathvariant="normal">蓝</mi></mstyle></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">\color{Blue}蓝</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback" style="color:Blue;">蓝</span></span></span></span><span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi mathvariant="normal">题</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">题</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord cjk_fallback">题</span></span></span></span>（手动捂脸</p>
<h1 id="例1">例1</h1>
<p><strong>题目：<a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P3367">P3367 【模板】并查集</a></strong></p>
<h2 id="思路">思路</h2>
<p>模板题，考虑用一个数组 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><msub><mi>a</mi><mi>i</mi></msub></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">fa_i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.8888799999999999em;vertical-align:-0.19444em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mord"><span class="mord mathdefault">a</span><span class="msupsub"><span class="vlist-t vlist-t2"><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.31166399999999994em;"><span style="top:-2.5500000000000003em;margin-left:0em;margin-right:0.05em;"><span class="pstrut" style="height:2.7em;"></span><span class="sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight"><span class="mord mathdefault mtight">i</span></span></span></span><span class="vlist-s">​</span></span><span class="vlist-r"><span class="vlist" style="height:0.15em;"><span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span> 记录 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span></span></span></span> 的负责人，函数 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>f</mi><mi>i</mi><mi>n</mi><mi>d</mi><mo>(</mo><mi>i</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">find(i)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault" style="margin-right:0.10764em;">f</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mord mathdefault">n</span><span class="mord mathdefault">d</span><span class="mopen">(</span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span><span class="mclose">)</span></span></span></span> 查询 <span class="katex"><span class="katex-mathml"><math><semantics><mrow><mi>i</mi></mrow><annotation encoding="application/x-tex">i</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class="katex-html" aria-hidden="true"><span class="base"><span class="strut" style="height:0.65952em;vertical-align:0em;"></span><span class="mord mathdefault">i</span></span></span></span> 的族长。</p>
<p>于是可以写</p>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">int find(int x){
    if(fa[x]==x) return x;//当查询到负责人时返回负责人
    return fa[x];
}
</code></pre>
<p>但这样貌似会超时。</p>
<p>于是需要<strong>路径压缩</strong>，如下图：</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://i.loli.net/2020/03/25/lSTvpJDanWoZRQe.png" alt="路径压缩.png" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>也就是说，在访问一个点的族长时把所有访问到的结点的负责人直接设为族长，像这样：</p>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">int find(int x){
    if(f[x]==x) return x;
    return f[x]=find(f[x]);
}
</code></pre>
<h2 id="代码">代码</h2>
<pre><code class="language-cpp">//P3367
#include &lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;
using namespace std;
int f[10010];
int find(int a){
    if(f[a]==a) return a;
    return f[a]=find(f[a]);
}
int main(){
    int n,m;
    cin&gt;&gt;n&gt;&gt;m;
    int x,y,z;
    for(int i=0;i&lt;=n;i++) f[i]=i;
    for(int i=0;i&lt;m;i++){
        cin&gt;&gt;z&gt;&gt;x&gt;&gt;y;
        if(z==1){
            f[find(x)]=find(y);
        }
        else{
            if(find(x)==find(y)) cout&lt;&lt;'Y'&lt;&lt;endl;
            else cout&lt;&lt;'N'&lt;&lt;endl;
        }
    }
    return 0;
}
</code></pre>
]]></content>
